  "title": "Japanese Culture",
  "description": "as the name suggests, adds japanese culture features to the game, and a new biome, japanese wisteria!",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/726/57/logo.png\" width=\"825\" height=\"464\">\n</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>About</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">a mod with japanese features,here are the principal features:<strong><br></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/J7xjqQXp/japaneseculture-barriers.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"45\"></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Japanese Wisteria (藤)</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">a new biome, the Japanese Wisteria Park, with large japanese wisteria flower trees in the cliffs</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/726/59/2023-09-07_17.png\" width=\"826\" height=\"405\"></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Tanuki (たぬき)</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">a new animal mob,its the Tanuki! (Or Raccoon Dog),a creature that lives in the forests,cherry groves and japanese wisteria park</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/726/61/2023-09-07_17.png\" width=\"826\" height=\"405\">\n  \n Oni (鬼)</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">a monster from the japanese mythology,have 4 variations. currently doesn't have a spawn</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/726/90/2023-09-07_19.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"826\" height=\"405\"></strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/J7xjqQXp/japaneseculture-barriers.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"45\"></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><br></strong></span></p>",
